title: Playboy - Tales Of Erotic Fantasies (1999) DVD5
description:
Director: T. Beck, Steve Conte, Bob Michaels 
Starring: Carrie Westcott, Ashlie Rhey, Dawn Raiya, Xaviera, Gwen Somers, Griffin Drew, Roxanna Michaels, Tammy Parks, Sean Abbananto, James Bonn, Jeff Eisenberger, Jeff Rector, Espen Tompter, Deiderik Van Nassan, Tim Holmes

Deep in the recesses of everyone's imagination lurk their most erotic fantasies. Playboy knows this, and has put together eight vignettes to illustrate these wildest carnal fantasies come true. The hottest and lustiest of all fetishistic and boundary-pushing imaginings come vividly to life in this collection of sexual yearning and fulfillment.
